snippet.title: Beloved Rapture - Official Gameplay Overview Trailer | Guerrilla Collective 2024
snippet.description: Get a peek into the mid-game content of Beloved Rapture, including how the world opens up, exploration, a look at the vast city of Alexandria, optional sidequests, coliseum battles, and more! Beloved Rapture will be available on PC, and a demo is available now. The demo gives access to the prologue, chapter one, and introduces the hero and more.
